17
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:37,469
(The missing wife appears) She is the one who suggested the kidnapping, Shiori

18
00:00:37,489 --> 00:00:40,310
Meeting Nanase Rin’s sister for the first time

19
00:00:41,571 --> 00:00:43,507
(date of kidnapping)

20
