Have you seen Xiao Lin?

30
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:11,402
There is no such auntie

31
00:01:11,905 --> 00:01:13,754
Don't you have any clues?

32
00:01:13,818 --> 00:01:16,581
You were the one who planned this kidnapping, right?

33
00:01:16,581 --> 00:01:17,875
Did you tell her?

34
00:01:18,110 --> 00:01:20,045
I've always wanted to ask

35
00:01:20,045 --> 00:01:22,045
Why did you choose my house?

36
00:01:22,088 --> 00:01:25,564
Did you kill my parents?

37
00:01:27,415 --> 00:01:30,575
Order to carry pistols

38
00:01:30,586 --> 00:01:33,091
On the premise of giving priority to the safety of the hostages

39
00:01:33,112 --> 00:01:34,759
Just in case of emergencies

40
00:01:34,780 --> 00:01:35,940
yes

41
00:01:36,892 --> 00:01:38,892
Pistol?

42
00:01:38,956 --> 00:01:43,170
