43
00:01:43,170 --> 00:01:46,052
A suspect in kidnapping and murder

44
00:01:46,180 --> 00:01:50,105
In short, if you catch Xinzhuang, you will know all the truth.

45
00:01:50,105 --> 00:01:51,424
yes

46
00:01:51,681 --> 00:01:54,511
OK, I'll tell you

47
00:01:54,693 --> 00:01:57,512
I picked your parents

48
00:01:57,651 --> 00:01:59,897
