94
00:04:27,523 --> 00:04:30,009
This is a souvenir from Singapore for you

95
00:04:36,453 --> 00:04:39,245
You still have time to hang out here

96
00:04:39,579 --> 00:04:41,912
The child hasn't been found yet

97
00:04:42,043 --> 00:04:45,846
Don't worry, you will definitely find her

98
00:04:46,178 --> 00:04:48,822
