99
00:04:48,989 --> 00:04:50,692
You are the one

100
00:04:51,381 --> 00:04:55,612
Do you understand how many interests and people are involved behind this matter?

101
00:04:57,328 --> 00:04:58,848
In case of failure

102
00:04:58,896 --> 00:05:02,161
You've lost more than just your Ph.D. status

103
00:05:06,417 --> 00:05:08,262
What is status?

104
00:05:11,127 --> 00:05:13,435
I bet my life

105
00:05:14,636 --> 00:05:17,762
Stop talking nonsense and go find that kid

106
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:20,339
Don't be preempted by the police

107
00:05:24,226 --> 00:05:26,784
I didn't mean to argue

108
00:05:28,195 --> 00:05:32,005
Let's live in peace with each other

109
00:06:00,153 --> 00:06:02,861
get up...

110
00:06:02,897 --> 00:06:05,128
Get up, get up, get up quickly

111
