What's your attitude? I woke you up out of kindness.

114
00:06:13,363 --> 00:06:16,075
-Won't you be gentler? -It's time to eat

115
00:06:17,714 --> 00:06:20,099
Please eat first

116
00:06:20,099 --> 00:06:22,214
Well, little Rin, let’s eat it too

117
00:06:23,129 --> 00:06:25,129
You eat first

118
