-How's it going? - It's so hot and delicious.

120
00:06:35,304 --> 00:06:36,647
No

121
00:06:36,665 --> 00:06:39,483
Will your tongue be numb or make you feel dizzy?

122
00:06:39,514 --> 00:06:41,611
ah? what are you talking about

123
00:06:41,611 --> 00:06:43,941
It's okay, eat quickly

124
00:06:52,289 --> 00:06:54,232
What are you doing again?

125
00:07:01,017 --> 00:07:03,017
I started

126
00:07:03,417 --> 00:07:07,353
Wow, this seasoning is too salty.

127
00:07:07,372 --> 00:07:09,201
Auntie, do you still have a sense of taste?

128
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,764
How about it

129
00:07:10,764 --> 00:07:13,900
I really miss the miso soup you cooked

130
00:07:13,922 --> 00:07:16,675
Do you like this taste?

131
00:07:16,686 --> 00:07:18,495
Relaxed physically and mentally

132
00:07:18,641 --> 00:07:20,191
delicious

133
00:07:20,806 --> 00:07:24,718
I'm going out to work later

134
00:07:24,998 --> 00:07:27,450
During this time, please stay at home.

135
00:07:27,450 --> 00:07:28,753
Yeah I will

136
00:07:28,753 --> 00:07:29,892
Did you hear Xiaolin?

137
00:07:30,553 --> 00:07:33,217
Auntie, I want to ask you a favor

138
00:07:33,217 --> 00:07:35,295
give me a mobile phone

139
00:07:35,306 --> 00:07:36,769
cell phone?

140
00:07:39,647 --> 00:07:42,355
Hello...

141
00:07:42,971 --> 00:07:44,859
Didn’t you say you should stay at home?

142
00:07:44,938 --> 00:07:47,855
I didn't agree

143
00:07:48,012 --> 00:07:49,867
It's dangerous to go outside

144
00:07:51,792 --> 00:07:53,104
of course i know

145
00:07:53,137 --> 00:07:56,893
But something more dangerous may happen if this continues

146
00:08:01,985 --> 00:08:05,275
Judging from your current income and expenditure...

147
00:08:05,324 --> 00:08:09,611
Efficient application and risk management are very important

148
00:08:09,634 --> 00:08:13,613
What is more dangerous to feed?

149
00:08:14,296 --> 00:08:16,870
You shouldn't be doubting Xi Li, right?

150
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,678
Reasons to doubt her

151
00:08:18,678 --> 00:08:21,396
More than not doubting her

152
00:08:26,295 --> 00:08:28,295
What do you want a cell phone for?

153
00:08:29,763 --> 00:08:33,418
The day of the kidnapping was July 8th

154
00:08:33,566 --> 00:08:36,828
Contemporaneous with the kidnapping

155
00:08:37,095 --> 00:08:40,716
Nanase and his wife were also killed

156
00:08:43,756 --> 00:08:48,028
The murder weapon that killed the dean was the samurai sword decorated in the house

157
00:08:48,258 --> 00:08:51,433
The wife is a letter opener

158
00:08:52,102 --> 00:08:55,634
Katana and letter opener...

159
00:08:55,772 --> 00:08:58,405
Do you see what they have in common?

160
00:08:59,809 --> 00:09:01,839
Completely different murder weapon

161
00:09:01,885 --> 00:09:06,443
Neither of these murder weapons were brought in from outside.

162
00:09:06,804 --> 00:09:08,804
I see

163
00:09:09,272 --> 00:09:10,984
so what

164
00:09:35,952 --> 00:09:38,499
Xiaolin, does your head hurt?

165
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:42,468
Did you remember something?

166
00:09:47,326 --> 00:09:49,326
Xiao Lin, this is...

167
00:09:49,985 --> 00:09:51,985
Monitor?

168
00:09:52,412 --> 00:09:54,342
Don't you think it's strange?

169
00:09:54,342 --> 00:09:56,290
Just call this monitor

170
00:09:56,309 --> 00:09:59,413
You should know what happened on the day of the murder, right?

171
00:10:00,276 --> 00:10:02,026
I see

172
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,797
You are right

173
00:10:04,888 --> 00:10:06,678
Do you really understand?

174
00:10:13,090 --> 00:10:14,672
please wait

175
00:10:14,802 --> 00:10:18,618
Sunouchi-senpai, this is Mr. Matsuda from the security company.

176
00:10:20,916 --> 00:10:22,163
-Ito-senpai-What's going on?

177
00:10:22,163 --> 00:10:23,732
There seemed to be some public quarrel yesterday

178
00:10:23,732 --> 00:10:26,941
This is the guard's body video, can you see it?

179
00:10:27,286 --> 00:10:29,154
Why don't you watch it yourself?

180
00:10:30,395 --> 00:10:32,635
Because you sit in my seat

181
00:10:32,635 --> 00:10:35,116
- Can you take a look? - What's going on?

182
00:10:35,276 --> 00:10:40,399
I have been a guard at Rongjin Memorial Hospital for a long time

183
00:10:40,547 --> 00:10:42,253
about a year ago

184
00:10:42,288 --> 00:10:46,684
Dean Nanase Mamoru asked me to serve as his residential security guard as well.

185
00:10:46,703 --> 00:10:49,214
How long is it?

186
00:10:49,214 --> 00:10:52,214
Plus one makes it thirty years faster

187
00:10:52,214 --> 00:10:55,342
Thirty years is really very senior.

188
00:10:55,389 --> 00:10:58,048
The dean must trust you very much

189
00:10:58,079 --> 00:11:00,222
Even ask you to be the security guard at the residence

190
00:11:00,222 --> 00:11:01,547
Don't dare to take it

191
00:11:01,563 --> 00:11:05,025
I personally rarely talk to the dean

192
00:11:05,041 --> 00:11:07,394
It should be based on my performance in the company.

193
00:11:08,187 --> 00:11:10,423
That's it, that's it

194
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,811
I want to ask

195
00:11:12,811 --> 00:11:17,170
Why were the monitors in the dean’s house removed?

196
00:11:17,182 --> 00:11:20,283
Yes, that was not long ago

197
00:11:20,324 --> 00:11:23,935
The dean asked me to dismantle it

198
00:11:23,958 --> 00:11:24,798
tear down?

199
00:11:24,795 --> 00:11:26,702
When was that?

200
00:11:26,702 --> 00:11:28,382
July 5th

201
00:11:28,975 --> 00:11:30,975
He said he wanted to switch to a monitor from another company.

202
00:11:30,975 --> 00:11:32,962
Ask me to dismantle the one I'm using now

203
00:11:34,187 --> 00:11:37,182
What about the previous images?

204
00:11:37,182 --> 00:11:42,586
The dean asked me to delete them all

205
00:11:42,632 --> 00:11:44,357
all?

206
00:11:44,403 --> 00:11:47,089
So nothing is left?

207
00:11:47,089 --> 00:11:49,730
Sorry I can't help

208
00:11:49,730 --> 00:11:51,337
It doesn't matter

209
00:11:51,519 --> 00:11:55,372
Can I go then?

210
00:11:55,577 --> 00:11:58,662
Okay, thank you for your cooperation

211
00:11:59,323 --> 00:12:01,323
I'll take you out

212
00:12:03,737 --> 00:12:05,440
Right

213
00:12:05,486 --> 00:12:08,172
Where were you on July 8th?

214
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,485
No. 8?

215
00:12:09,485 --> 00:12:11,142
This is a routine inquiry

216
00:12:11,142 --> 00:12:15,480
I patrol the hospital as usual from morning to six o'clock in the evening

217
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:18,922
Go see your high school classmates after get off work

218
00:12:18,922 --> 00:12:21,563
The two drank until morning

219
00:12:21,769 --> 00:12:26,167
Can you give us the name and contact information of that friend?

220
00:12:26,167 --> 00:12:27,635
OK

221
00:12:29,434 --> 00:12:31,297
so unlucky

222
00:12:31,297 --> 00:12:34,317
Maybe we can know the truth if we have surveillance video.

223
00:12:35,624 --> 00:12:37,832
Do you think it's a coincidence?

224
00:12:39,517 --> 00:12:42,852
Murders and kidnappings occurred immediately after the monitors were removed

225
00:12:42,852 --> 00:12:45,676
And none of the previous files have been left behind.

226
00:12:45,858 --> 00:12:48,967
It is indeed too beneficial for the murderer

227
00:12:48,967 --> 00:12:51,196
Sunouchi-senpai, please take a look.

228
00:12:51,196 --> 00:12:55,256
There seemed to be a fight in the West District yesterday

229
00:12:56,098 --> 00:12:58,784
I don’t know if this is a body-worn video.

230
00:12:59,422 --> 00:13:02,161
Could this person be...

231
00:13:02,161 --> 00:13:04,093
It's him

232
00:13:09,514 --> 00:13:12,200
Hello, is that okay?

233
00:13:12,474 --> 00:13:14,634
It's time for us to go back

234
00:13:14,702 --> 00:13:17,343
By the way, what is your relationship?

235
00:13:18,596 --> 00:13:20,551
You and aunt

236
00:13:20,583 --> 00:13:23,446
Your personalities are completely different

237
00:13:23,446 --> 00:13:25,407
How do we know each other?

238
00:13:25,407 --> 00:13:27,270
So what if we know each other?

239
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:31,492
Where did you first meet? Who spoke to you first?

240
00:13:31,525 --> 00:13:34,076
Is it you or her?

241
00:13:34,576 --> 00:13:37,972
-Who confesses first? -You are the gossip reporter.

242
00:13:39,019 --> 00:13:40,476
haven't seen you for a long time

243
00:13:40,476 --> 00:13:42,476
i have been waiting for you

244
00:13:42,476 --> 00:13:44,295
- Come over there - OK

245
00:13:48,691 --> 00:13:52,842
Who is he smiling so happily?

246
00:13:53,016 --> 00:13:57,258
So when and where did you meet?

247
00:13:57,919 --> 00:14:02,023
When I was a child, I was in a kindergarten

248
00:14:02,388 --> 00:14:05,175
Neither Xili nor I have parents

249
00:14:06,106 --> 00:14:10,706
I used to be a crybaby and a clumsy person

250
00:14:10,814 --> 00:14:15,257
Xiori is very reliable and smart.

251
00:14:15,873 --> 00:14:19,276
She often teaches me how to read

252
00:14:19,276 --> 00:14:22,603
Will also play with me

253
00:14:22,625 --> 00:14:25,250
- It seems - It seems?

254
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:27,891
I don't remember much about that time.

255
00:14:27,959 --> 00:14:30,977
I get a headache every time I think about it

256
00:14:31,638 --> 00:14:35,401
Definitely not a good memory

257
00:14:40,068 --> 00:14:43,510
Our fate has been with us since then

258
00:14:44,085 --> 00:14:45,426
Do you want to eat?

259
00:14:46,766 --> 00:14:48,213
If you don’t want it, don’t want it.

260
00:14:56,384 --> 00:14:57,123
How about it

261
00:14:57,123 --> 00:14:58,621
