266
00:15:19,147 --> 00:15:20,307
she's gone

267
00:15:20,322 --> 00:15:21,725
Follow up quickly

268
00:15:22,565 --> 00:15:24,109
It's a university hospital

269
00:15:24,235 --> 00:15:25,692
hurry up

270
