271
00:15:31,579 --> 00:15:33,367
Needless to say

272
00:15:33,414 --> 00:15:35,705
Shiori wouldn't do that...

273
00:15:35,721 --> 00:15:37,179
who knows

274
00:15:37,179 --> 00:15:40,894
We are nominally husband and wife, but you have been living apart.

275
